<div class="w3-content w3-section" style="max-width:500px">
  <p>The w3-animate-fading class animates an element in and out (takes about 10 seconds).</p>

  <div class="w3-display-container mySlides">
  <img src="http://www.clocalltoaction.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/See-Local-To-Action-www.clocalltoaction.com-World-travel-blog-family-holiday-vacation-website-Macho-Picchu-Place-To-Visit-In-South-America.jpg" style="width:90%">
